data.description:
Priced to sell quickly, move-in ready+. Great updated home sitting on 3 lots with many additional options to make the home your own. Well maintained with concrete inner walls, updated appliances and new flooring throughout. Brand new updated kitchen with new cabinets, butcher block countertops and appliances. Remodeled spa bathroom with soaking tub and split barn doors. New luxury ceiling fans in every room. Roof was replaced in 2020 w/warranty. Carport has been enclosed creating additional bedroom/ office, large yard with underground fencing for pets. New well maintained mature landscaping with gorgeous white stone walkway to front entrance. Dining area could easily be enclosed to create 4th bedroom/office. Fresh Benjamin Moore paint throughout. Small shed out back for additional storage. Great sun exposure provides lots of natural light and is perfect if you wanted to go solar. Not far from Leland and Whiteville with quick access to 74/76 and only 4 miles from Lake Waccamaw for excellent fishing, canoeing, and boating. 

+ Willing to negotiate to have existing furniture remain, if desired.
++Patio blocks on premises for small patio, BBQ area, or fire pit. Additional padding and flooring as well.
+++Canoe is staying for your water pleasure adventures.
data.whatILove: Extremely quiet neighborhood with great neighbors. Close proximity to Lake Waccamaw.
